                                                                            <li>Coins will be deposited immediately after
                                                                                <span class='min_conf text-info loader_12'>20</span> network confirmation</li>
                                                                            <li class='contract_address_box ' style='display:none'>
                                                                                <span class='coin_name text-info loader_12'>---</span> Contract address :
                                                                                <span class="contract_address text-info"></span>
                                                                            </li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        </p>

                                                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="col-md-4 pt-3 text-center">
